  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PASemantics

    public class InvolutaryPASemantics
extends AbstractPASemantics
    P is involutary wrt. AF if for every A,B in Arg, if A->B then P(A)=1-P(B).
    Author:
    Matthias Thimm
